videos.description: Oregon's Tony Brooks-James fumbles near the end zone, and Southern Utah's Taylor Nelson recovers.
videos.headline: Thunderbirds recover Ducks' fumble at goal line

videos.description: Oregon defenders knock the ball out of the receiver's hands and catch the deflection for an interception.
videos.headline: Ducks punch ball loose to intercept pass

videos.description: Royce Freeman finds the end zone from 3 yards out to give Oregon a 28-7 lead.
videos.headline: Freeman runs it in for Oregon TD

videos.description: Kani Benoit outruns the Southern Utah defenders to score a 29-yard rushing touchdown.
videos.headline: Benoit breaks free for second TD of the game

videos.description: Royce Freeman eludes the Thunderbird defenders to score his second touchdown of the quarter.
videos.headline: Freeman finds end zone again on 16-yard scamper

videos.description: QB Patrick Tyler buys time in the pocket and finds Landen Measom who takes it all the way to the house for a 64-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Tyler connects with Measom for long Thunderbird TD

videos.description: Ducks' Tony Brooks-James can't handle the kickoff and the Thunderbirds win the scramble to recover the ball.
videos.headline: Oregon fumbles kickoff, Southern Utah recovers

videos.description: James Felila can't find a hole in the line, so he improvises and scores a 4-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Thunderbirds' Felila scores on second effort

videos.description: Royce Freeman's big game continues as he scores his third touchdown, this time from 13 yards out.
videos.headline: Freeman finds pay dirt for his 3rd TD of game

videos.description: Justin Herbert lofts a deep pass to Charles Nelson who dives and comes up with the catch for a huge gain.
videos.headline: Oregon's Nelson lays out to make 50-yard grab

videos.description: Charles Nelson runs it in from 2 yards out to give Oregon a 56-21 lead.
videos.headline: Oregon piles it on with 6th rushing TD

videos.description: Southern Utah's Elijah Holt trips over his teammate while returning a kickoff, and is forced from the game with a leg injury.
videos.headline: Thunderbirds' Holt carted off after gruesome injury

videos.description: Despite a defensive pass interference call, Oregon's Johnny Johnson III contorts his body to make a great catch.
videos.headline: Ducks' Johnson makes acrobatic catch

videos.description: Kani Benoit finishes the Ducks' drive from a yard out.
videos.headline: Oregon drops 70 with 8th rushing TD

videos.description: Oregon sets a modern-day school record for points in a game on Taylor Alie's 4-yard TD run.
videos.headline: Ducks score 11th TD of game
